Interface UserProfile

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractUserProfile, AccountUserRepresentationUserProfile, AttributeUserProfile, IdpUserProfile, UserModelUserProfile, UserRepresentationUserProfile

    public interface UserProfile
    Abstraction, which allows to update the user in various contexts (Required action of already existing user, or first identity provider login when user doesn't yet exists in Keycloak DB)
